Seiko's Marine Master is a full-fledged professional diver's model with 1000m water resistance. Equipped with a mechanical movement caliber 8L35 dedicated to diver's watches. The ultra-airtight one-piece structure boasts high airtightness and watertightness, and it is waterproof for 300m saturation diving that allows deep-sea diving, and is equipped with magnetic resistance of 4,800A/m. This is the Mobile Suit Gundam 40th Anniversary mass-produced Zaku limited model. The coloring of the mass-produced Zaku and the characteristic font of 1000M water resistance make it a valuable limited edition that will tickle the hearts of fans.

There are some small scratches, but it is in a beautiful state. With box and warranty.

Use plastic bottles are collected.The plastic bottles are then shredded into small pieces.The pieces are selectively hand arranged & then pressed into a panel.
